<div class="container-fluid spacer">
  <div class="row user-row">
    <div class="col col-lg-3 mt-5 left-group">
      <div class="profile-picture d-flex justify-content-center mb-4">
        <% if current_user.profile_picture.nil? || current_user.profile_picture == "" %>
          <%= image_tag "https://res.cloudinary.com/isep/image/upload/v1577132733/unify/download_wqralk.png", class: "avatar" %>
        <% else %>
          <%= image_tag current_user.profile_picture, class: "avatar-img" %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="infos text-center pb-3">
        <h2><%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></h2>
        <ul class="mt-3">
          <li><span>Mail ISEP : </span><%= @user.email %></li>
          <li><span>Promo : </span><%= @user.promotion %></li>
          <li><span>Section : </span><%= @user.section %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col col-lg-9 right-group">
      <div class="row justify-content-center p-2">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="family-banner">
            <img src="https://i.imgur.com/kBFDFIW.jpg"/>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row p-2">
        <div class="col-9">
          <div class="white-wrapper mb-4">
            <% if @user.clubs.nil? || @user.clubs == [] %>
              <h3 class="text-center">Membre d'aucune association</h3>
            <% else %>
              <h3>Associations</h3>
              <div class="assos d-flex justify-content-start pb-3">
                <% @user.clubs.each do |club| %>
                    <%= link_to club_path(club), :title => club.name do %>
                      <div class="button-effect-3 <%= club.name.parameterize.underscore %>">
                          <%= image_tag club.logo, class:"club-logo" %>
                      </div>
                    <% end %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="white-wrapper d-flex flex-column align-items-start mb-4">
            <h3>Modification du profil</h3>
            <%= link_to "#", class:"button-effect-4" do %>
              <span>Modifier ma photo</span>
              <i class="fas fa-image"></i>
            <% end %>
            <%= link_to "#", class:"button-effect-4" do %>
              <span>Modifier mon mot de passe</span>
              <i class="fas fa-key"></i>
            <% end %>
            <%= link_to "#", class:"button-effect-4" do %>
              <span>Enregistrer</span>
              <i class="far fa-save"></i>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-3">
          <h2>Biographie</h2>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Mauris consequat, tortor sed vestibulum lacinia, libero nibh imperdiet lectus, nec maximus elit arcu vel nisi. Aenean quis accumsan odio. Quisque porta sodales ligula at sagittis. Quisque consectetur pellentesque condimentum. Vestibulum imperdiet molestie pellentesque. Praesent eget augue ac turpis fringilla elementum.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%= javascript_pack_tag 'shared/navbar' %>